('95075','32790','5','Holiday house in a popular residential complex, Nova Santa Ponsa for sale or rent'),
('95076','32791','5','The house stands on an approximately 600sqm plot with landscaped garden and private pool with views of the adjacent golf course Santa Ponsa II. The 195m² living space is spread over 2 floors. On the ground floor there is an entrance area, a living-dining room with fireplace, kitchen, utility room, guest toilet and 1 bedroom with bathroom en suite. On the 1st floor has 2 more bedrooms (with terrace), each with a bathroom en suite. Facilities include air conditioning  w / c and a fitted kitchen. The house with 2 car parking spaces will be sold unfurnished. The condominium offers 2 outdoor pools and even a 25m indoor swimming pool.\r\nRent: 2.400 € / month including pool and garden maintenance, 6 months rent in advance, 2 rent deposit. Minimum rental period 1 year. Broker Fee: 1.5 times the monthly rent\r\n'),
